title: Kate Kennedy - The Deep End

description:
My HoneyDew this week is Kate Kennedy! Kate didn’t get into grad school which is partially how she ended up doing porn and Kate jumped right into the deep end! Kate opens up about her time as a porn star and some of the outrageous things she’s had to do on camera! In Kate’s first scene, she was tied up and hung upside down and she was once waterboarded - and those are just a coupla examples! Check out her story!
